F.
Provide for a diversity of housing opportunities;
G. Facilitate the adequate provision of transportation, water, sewerage, schools,
parks, recreation, emergency services, and other public facilities;
H.
Maintain and enhance the character of certain districts within the Town
through an emphasis on design quality;
I.
Maintain and protect a high quality of aesthetic standards for development;
